commit.message: Added clear votes button, changed functionality slightly
Updated code to only send data once per second
Updated frontend to only allow one vote per 3 mins
Updated christmas thing with new MQTT server
Added function to allow system to work with only 1 piece of voting data
Added code to delete all votes
Added code to insert a blank question into the DB if there is not one present and a GET request is performed
Added auth for admin system, added reading from environment vars for DB, MQTT, and auth details
Implemented admin system, made many front and back end changes
Rewrote LED code to use smoothing
Added christmas code, updated server-side stuff with votes DB
Merged frontend (messy for now), moved API endpoints
Started work on server, as well as a test front end for socket.io
